Description: Minecraft server tools for Proxmox LXC (Java & Bedrock)
 Streamlined helper commands to create, copy, manage, and back up Minecraft servers
 in Proxmox LXC containers. Bridge-only networking, static IPs, thin-provisioned disks,
 daily backups (vzdump), CTID=Port policy, and auto-detected Java/Bedrock installs.
